race.comment: ELLEN ROSE (1) finds it hard to win. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (19.07) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Must come into calculations. I'M A DANDY (3) missed the frame last time at this track but the start prior rocketed around 300m at this track in 16.61. Top win two back and can measure up again. DUAL JEWEL (7) last start finished 3rd on October 2 over 350m at this track behind Finest Cut beaten 2.5 lengths (19.73) in a Grade 5. Can feature in the finish. HEAD WEST (2) is worth consideration.
